snippet.title: The Chase
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Official YouTube channel for The Chase!

Watch your favourite highlights, discover exclusive content and get full access to unseen behind-the-scenes footage featuring Bradley and the Chasers. Make sure you subscribe to never miss a thing!

The Chase is on!

Apply now to be a contestant on the show.
https://www.itv.com/beontv/thechase/
